description: The HpeiLOGUIService resource describes properties used by the BMC Graphical User Interface.

Features.description: Contains the authentication information for the external service.

AhsViewer.description: This property indicates whether Active Health System Viewer feature is enabled on this platform.

AnonymousData.description: This property indicates whether Anonymous Data feature is enabled on this platform.

BiosPrivilege.description: This property indicates whether Host BIOS privilege is enabled on this platform.

CacSmartcard.description: This property indicates whether Certificate Authentication feature is enabled on this platform.

ComputeCloudConsoleFlag.description: This property indicates whether Compute Cloud Console Feature is enabled.

CoolingModuleSupport.description: This property indicates whether Liquid Cooling modules are available on this platform.

DotNetConsole.description: This property indicates whether Remote console feature is enabled on this platform.

EAPTLSSupport.description: This property indicates whether 802.1X feature is supported on this platform.

Encryption.description: This property indicates whether Encryption feature is enabled on this platform.

EventDetails.description: This property indicates whether Event Details feature is enabled on this platform.

ExternalMonitor.description: This property indicates whether Server Health on External Monitor feature is enabled on this platform.

Federation.description: This property indicates whether Federation feature is enabled on this platform.

HighEfficiencyMode.description: This property indicates whether High Efficiency Mode on redundant power supply is enabled on this platform.

HostNicPrivilege.description: This property indicates whether Host NIC Privilege is enabled on this platform.

IntelligentProvisioning.description: This property indicates whether Intelligent Provisioning is enabled on this platform.

IpManager.description: This property indicates whether the BMC is managed by Remote Manager software.

IpxeBoot.description: This property indicates Embedded iPXE boot option is enabled on this platform.

UefiSerialDbgMsg.description: This property indicates Uefi Serial debug Message option is enabled on this platform.

JavaConsole.description: This property indicates whether Java based Remote console feature is enabled on this platform.

Kerberos.description: This property indicates whether Kerberos authentication feature is enabled on this platform.

Licensing.description: This property indicates whether Licensing feature is enabled on this platform.

Mobile.description: This property indicates whether Mobile view feature is enabled on this platform.

PowerDiscovery.description: This property indicates whether HPE Power Discovery Service feature is enabled on this platform.

RecoverySet.description: This property indicates whether Recovery Set privilege is enabled on this platform.

RemoteConsoleSecurity.description: This property indicates whether Remote Console Security feature is enabled on this platform.

RemoteSupport.description: This property indicates whether Remote Support feature is enabled on this platform.

Repository.description: This property indicates whether Repository feature is enabled on this platform.

RIBCL.description: This property indicates whether RIBCL feature is enabled on this platform.

SecurityDashboard.description: This property indicates whether Security Dashboard feature is enabled on this platform.

ServiceAccount.description: This property indicates whether Service Account feature is enabled on this platform.

SingleSignOn.description: This property indicates whether Single Sign-On (SSO) feature is enabled on this platform.

StoragePrivilege.description: This property indicates whether Host Storage privilege is enabled on this platform.

SwapROM.description: This property indicates whether Swap ROM feature is enabled on this platform.

SharedNicOcp.description: This property indicates whether SNP device is an NC-SI compliant Open Computing Project 3.0 or later NIC.

SystemAutoHeal.description: This property indicates whether Intelligent Diagnostics feature is enabled on this platform.

SystemDefaults.description: This property indicates whether System Defaults feature is enabled on this platform.

ThermalGraph.description: This property indicates whether Power Meter feature is enabled on this platform.

Thumbnail.description: This property indicates whether Thumbnail feature is enabled on this platform.

UpdateService.description: This property indicates whether Firmware update feature is enabled on this platform.

VirtualMedia.description: This property indicates whether Virtual Media feature is enabled on this platform.

TreeList.description: A static format for the navigation panel in the BMC Graphical User Interface.

Features.description: The name of the feature associated with the navigation link.

LangKey.description: The localization key in reference to the navigation link.

Link.longDescription: The name of the HTML file for this navigation link.

TabSet.description: The name of the navigation item linked with the tabs.

Tabs.description: A static array of tabs linked with the navigation item.

Features.description: The name of the feature associated with the tab.

LangKey.description: The localization key in reference to the name of the tab.

Link.description: The name of the HTML file for this tab.

Text.description: The default text used for this tab.
The default text used for this navigation link.
